:.START

Before I welcome Nicholas McInnes Jr. 18 letter wey dey drop correction for your "World Wide Tax" table (editorial page, Aug. 29) I dey surprised sey e ignore oder mistake wey some of us dey miss for house.

As I be channel islander, I con dey wonder sey my birth place wey dey inside di 86 countries with income tax, despite di history of di local goment, my passport clear sey na Birsh citizen o, wheder na MR. MCInnes oversight na just sign of any mainlander wey be sey na mainlander, and friends on top Isle of Man na im go continue to dey ponder.

Nicholas Basham

Huston

